            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>cornflour</strong> (save the rest for later!), your <strong>soy sauce</strong> and 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[5 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong> in a bowl and stir it all together</p><p>Add your <strong>Chinese rice wine </strong>and <strong>honey</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> honey sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1633431127515-x200.jpg",
