          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1633431186482-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> General Tso's basa</strong> over the<strong> cooked rice </strong>with the <strong>broccoli</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
